lead_paragraph: Mike Conley scored 24 points, Marc Gasol added 18 and the Memphis Grizzlies overcame a slow start for a 102-98 victory over the Minnesota Timberwolves on Wednesday night in the season opener for both teams.

headline.print_headline: Conley, Gasol Lead Grizzlies Over Timberwolves 102-98
